0 -14 Td
(XETA is a lightweight direct-to-consumer e-commerce platform where small sellers can list) Tj
0 -14 Td
(computer peripherals and consumers can browse, order, and pay with cash-on-delivery \(COD\). The) Tj
0 -14 Td
(platform aims for quick time-to-list for sellers, a clean buying flow for customers, and a) Tj
0 -14 Td
(minimal admin interface for order processing.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(Primary differentiator: simple seller onboarding and COD-focused checkout adapted to local) Tj
0 -14 Td
(preferences.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
